title: Student creates water-colour paints made from discarded cosmetics
text:
Student creates water-colour paints made from discarded cosmetics Wednesday, May 23, 2018 - 02:09
A British university student has created a range of water-colour paints made from discarded cosmetics, which she calls an example of how the so-called 'circular economy' can help improve the environment. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
